import React from 'react'
import { Box ,Button} from '@mui/material'
import { CreateOutlined } from '@mui/icons-material'

function SideBarContent() {
  return (
    <Box>
      
        <Button>
            <CreateOutlined>Compose</CreateOutlined>
        </Button>
      
      <Box></Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default SideBarContent
